1
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:26,760
Mr. Paisal fell ill and died

2
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:29,720
because you poisoned him?

3
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:31,160
I'm really sorry, Un.

4
00:02:35,560 --> 00:02:38,720
I'll kill Yai
and wash Aunt Un's feet with his blood.

5
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,040
Without Aunt Un,

6
00:03:03,040 --> 00:03:04,680
how will you carry on?

7
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:08,280
I'm really worried about you.

8
00:03:09,840 --> 00:03:11,160
I'll manage.

9
00:03:20,640 --> 00:03:21,800
Can I…

10
00:03:23,600 --> 00:03:25,360
be your big brother?

11
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:42,200
Miss On. Miss On, please wait.

12
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:44,480
Barging into a funeral pavilion
would be inappropriate.

13
00:03:44,560 --> 00:03:46,120
We should wait here.

14
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,840
Who cares?!

15
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,360
My fiancé is having an affair.

16
00:03:49,440 --> 00:03:51,120
Why would I care about being polite?

17
00:03:51,200 --> 00:03:52,160
Back off.

18
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:54,400
Miss On. Miss On, wait.

19
00:03:54,480 --> 00:03:57,560
I was terrible and selfish.

20
00:03:58,160 --> 00:04:00,320
What I did is unforgivable.

21
00:04:01,320 --> 00:04:05,840
But it's in the past,
which I can't change.

22
00:04:08,720 --> 00:04:10,240
I want to be by your side,

23
00:04:11,720 --> 00:04:13,440
supporting you

24
00:04:15,560 --> 00:04:19,240
as a brother
who truly cares about his sister.

25
00:04:32,440 --> 00:04:33,640
I caught you in the act.

26
00:04:33,720 --> 00:04:35,640
Pin, you shameless bitch.

27
00:04:36,280 --> 00:04:38,080
Even with your mom's corpse
lying in that coffin,

28
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:40,480
you still couldn't resist messing around
with someone's man.

29
00:04:40,560 --> 00:04:41,680
On?

30
00:04:42,680 --> 00:04:44,360
Pin. I'll kill you!

31
00:04:44,440 --> 00:04:46,440
- On!
- I'll kill you!

32
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,560
- On, let go.
- Miss On, please stop.

33
00:04:48,640 --> 00:04:49,880
- Don't stop me, Jan!
- On.

34
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:53,200
You love her so much?!

35
00:04:56,000 --> 00:04:59,080
- How dare you cheat on me? How dare you!
- On!

36
00:04:59,160 --> 00:05:01,160
- How could you do this to me?!
- On. Stop.

37
00:05:01,240 --> 00:05:02,600
- On!
- Hey, hey.

38
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:04,760
- On.
- Why did you hurt Na?

39
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,800
Miss On.

40
00:05:09,240 --> 00:05:10,560
Why did you slap me?

41
00:05:11,600 --> 00:05:12,840
Do you know who I am?!

42
00:05:13,440 --> 00:05:15,520
You're just a child of disgraced elites.

43
00:05:15,600 --> 00:05:18,240
You're lucky Na
even considered marrying you.

44
00:05:18,320 --> 00:05:20,520
How could you say that to her?

45
00:05:20,600 --> 00:05:23,200
Just you wait.
I'll expose your plan to trick Mr. Tong.

46
00:05:23,280 --> 00:05:24,760
Do it! I dare you!

47
00:05:25,600 --> 00:05:28,760
Do you really think
I'm the only one he will go after?

48
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,160
Shut your mouth, Jan.

49
00:05:33,440 --> 00:05:34,880
Pin hugged Na.

50
00:05:34,960 --> 00:05:36,520
She's trying to take him from me.

51
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,160
How am I supposed to tolerate that?

52
00:05:40,840 --> 00:05:43,280
I was just comforting Pin.

53
00:05:43,960 --> 00:05:45,600
And On misunderstood us.

54
00:05:45,680 --> 00:05:47,640
Why don't you just go sleep with her?

55
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:48,640
Enough!

56
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:50,840
Can you stop?

57
00:05:51,480 --> 00:05:54,560
Can you please just let me
send off my mother in peace?

58
00:05:55,640 --> 00:05:58,640
Get out! All of you, get out!

59
00:06:05,000 --> 00:06:07,560
Well, what are you all looking at?

60
00:06:07,640 --> 00:06:10,720
Go to the farm and get back to work. Go!

61
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:12,320
- Yes, yes.
- Go.

62
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,960
Let's go.

63
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:17,800
- Let's go, On.
- Pin.

64
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:29,360
This is Madam Krongsuk.

65
00:06:31,080 --> 00:06:32,000
Hello, ma'am.

66
00:06:32,800 --> 00:06:34,840
Yes, Officer.
Can I help you with something?

67
00:06:34,920 --> 00:06:38,800
I'd like to question you
regarding the death of Ms. Unreuan.

68
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,280
I hadn't seen Un

69
00:06:49,880 --> 00:06:52,200
since Yai and Pload

70
00:06:52,280 --> 00:06:55,320
threatened to kill me
and I had to flee the farm.

71
00:06:57,200 --> 00:06:59,280
They were like mad dogs.

72
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:03,280
They accused Un and Pin
of conspiring with me,

73
00:07:04,440 --> 00:07:07,360
so they killed Un as an act of revenge.

74
00:07:08,520 --> 00:07:10,440
Didn't you say that your husband

75
00:07:10,520 --> 00:07:12,720
never had conflicts with the deceased?

76
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:20,720
Oh, Pload has tons of men working for him.

77
00:07:21,280 --> 00:07:23,320
If Pin said too much,

78
00:07:23,400 --> 00:07:26,280
he would send someone
to silence her, Officer.

79
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:28,240
Is that true, Pin?

80
00:07:30,840 --> 00:07:32,720
This is my mother's funeral.

81
00:07:33,840 --> 00:07:35,640
I'm not ready to give any statement.

82
00:07:37,080 --> 00:07:39,680
Please give her some time to mourn.

83
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:46,880
Oh, who could possibly endure
their own husband murdering their mother?

84
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,040
Poor girl.

85
00:07:55,960 --> 00:07:58,480
Right now, Mr. Pload is refusing to speak.

86
00:07:59,480 --> 00:08:01,560
Can you think of any other witnesses?

87
00:08:04,440 --> 00:08:05,920
Other witnesses?

88
00:08:08,680 --> 00:08:10,160
I can think of one.

89
00:08:12,120 --> 00:08:13,360
Why are you walking away?

90
00:08:13,440 --> 00:08:15,480
Just stop and talk to me.

91
00:08:16,920 --> 00:08:17,800
I'm tired of you.

92
00:08:17,880 --> 00:08:19,960
And who started it?

93
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:22,760
- You're greedy and never satisfied.
- See?

94
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:25,600
You pick a fight every time
I open my mouth.

95
00:08:25,680 --> 00:08:27,520
So I'd rather stay silent.

96
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:31,160
- If I find out you're still with Pinanong…
- What?

97
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,799
What are you going to do to me?

98
00:08:37,120 --> 00:08:40,840
I won't do anything to you,
but I'll do something to her.

99
00:09:14,880 --> 00:09:15,840
Hey.

100
00:09:39,640 --> 00:09:41,600
Hey, who are you running from?

101
00:09:42,640 --> 00:09:44,400
Just keep driving. No need to talk.

102
00:09:44,920 --> 00:09:46,240
If you don't want to die too.

103
00:09:56,040 --> 00:09:58,040
Mr. Yai, please hang in there.

104
00:09:58,560 --> 00:10:00,200
Where should I drive you?

105
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,360
A hospital, obviously. He's about to die!

106
00:10:03,440 --> 00:10:05,120
Uh, wait…

107
00:10:06,400 --> 00:10:08,240
Call the village chief for me.

108
00:10:09,120 --> 00:10:10,240
Village chief?

109
00:10:11,000 --> 00:10:12,680
What village chief?

110
00:10:22,720 --> 00:10:25,360
Hey, Mr. Yai. Don't get up yet.

111
00:10:25,440 --> 00:10:28,400
- Oh, sorry.
- Let go. These wounds are nothing.

112
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:43,400
Take off your shirt,
so I can wipe you down.

113
00:10:43,480 --> 00:10:44,760
No need.

114
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:49,200
What? Then how am I supposed
to wipe you down?

115
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,160
Come on, I'll do it for you.

116
00:10:52,520 --> 00:10:54,240
I said no need. Do you want to die?

117
00:10:54,320 --> 00:10:58,280
Mr. Yai, I'm the one who saved your life.

118
00:10:58,360 --> 00:10:59,240
And now what?

119
00:10:59,320 --> 00:11:01,080
You don't even want to repay me?

120
00:11:02,160 --> 00:11:04,680
At least a little kiss.

121
00:11:05,400 --> 00:11:06,880
Take this.

122
00:11:06,960 --> 00:11:08,720
Look at you.

123
00:11:08,800 --> 00:11:09,680
You're a woman.

124
00:11:09,760 --> 00:11:11,240
Have some dignity, will you?

125
00:11:11,320 --> 00:11:13,360
- It hurts, Auntie!
- Here.

126
00:11:14,520 --> 00:11:18,080
I told you, call me Chief Yam.

127
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:21,800
And don't ever come into this room
and mess with Yai again.

128
00:11:21,880 --> 00:11:23,320
He has a wife.

129
00:11:23,840 --> 00:11:25,200
A wife?

130
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:29,600
That's old news from ages ago.

131
00:11:29,680 --> 00:11:33,800
Mr. Yai and Pin already separated.

132
00:11:33,880 --> 00:11:36,040
You're not really up-to-date, Chief.

133
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:38,600
Is that true?

134
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:40,400
You can leave now.

135
00:11:41,920 --> 00:11:42,760
Go.

136
00:11:44,200 --> 00:11:45,320
He wants you to leave. Go.

137
00:11:51,640 --> 00:11:52,880
Is that true?

138
00:11:52,960 --> 00:11:54,760
You already broke up with Pinanong?

139
00:11:58,080 --> 00:12:01,840
I knew it. A nice woman like her
wouldn't be able to tolerate you.

140
00:12:05,880 --> 00:12:07,800
She's taking Pin's side, huh?

141
00:12:12,120 --> 00:12:14,240
It's unlikely that Pin and I
will ever be the same.

142
00:12:15,200 --> 00:12:17,040
Have you been able to contact
Uncle Pload and Pan?

143
00:12:17,120 --> 00:12:19,720
I've called them. No one answered,

144
00:12:19,800 --> 00:12:22,640
so I sent someone from the village
that I can trust to investigate.

145
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:25,520
By the way, tell me everything.

146
00:12:25,600 --> 00:12:28,480
Why were you running away from the police,

147
00:12:28,560 --> 00:12:30,720
and how did you end up here
with that witch's niece?

148
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:32,080
What happened?

149
00:12:45,080 --> 00:12:45,960
Dad.

150
00:12:46,040 --> 00:12:47,480
Pan.

151
00:12:47,560 --> 00:12:50,800
Hey, where the hell were you?

152
00:12:50,880 --> 00:12:52,800
Why are you only showing up now?

153
00:12:55,760 --> 00:12:58,960
That day, you told me to wait in the car,
but I couldn't wait any longer.

154
00:13:01,760 --> 00:13:03,640
We need to get out of here

155
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:05,520
and wait for confirmation
that Yai's been dealt with.

156
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:08,680
Then, we can go take control
of Paisal Farm. Go.

157
00:13:11,400 --> 00:13:13,040
Mr. Pan, please don't. It's me.

158
00:13:13,560 --> 00:13:14,480
Where's Dad?

159
00:13:14,560 --> 00:13:16,480
Don't ask me now. We need to run.

160
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:26,080
<i>Luckily, Aunt Pen and Uncle Win caught on</i>

161
00:13:26,160 --> 00:13:28,440
<i>and got out of the farm</i>
<i>before Tong found them.</i>

162
00:13:28,520 --> 00:13:31,760
<i>And they called me,</i>
<i>so I told Phong and Uncle Win</i>

163
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:35,920
<i>to take Aunt Pen back to the mine,</i>
<i>since it's the safest place, Dad.</i>

164
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:43,680
You did great, Pan.

165
00:13:45,640 --> 00:13:48,840
Dad, I'll do everything to bail you out.

166
00:13:49,440 --> 00:13:51,440
The lawyer is taking care of it.

167
00:13:52,120 --> 00:13:55,200
Pan, don't worry about me.

168
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:58,840
You need to go find Mr. Yai

169
00:13:59,360 --> 00:14:01,440
and see whether he's alive or not.

170
00:14:02,640 --> 00:14:04,880
You must bring Mr. Yai home.

171
00:14:04,960 --> 00:14:06,320
Yes, Dad.

172
00:14:10,280 --> 00:14:14,520
I think it's easier

173
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:16,360
to prepare for his funeral, Pload.

174
00:14:16,440 --> 00:14:18,920
You! Madam.

175
00:14:20,120 --> 00:14:23,680
Remember this. Once I get out of here,

176
00:14:23,760 --> 00:14:26,240
you and Tong

177
00:14:26,320 --> 00:14:28,320
had better get your coffins ready.

178
00:14:29,680 --> 00:14:33,240
You should worry about yourself
and your mine first.

179
00:14:33,320 --> 00:14:34,720
What's that supposed to mean?

180
00:14:37,800 --> 00:14:38,880
Close it up.

181
00:15:10,320 --> 00:15:13,360
Dad, Aunt Pen texted me.

182
00:15:14,280 --> 00:15:16,400
She said the mine was ordered
to close temporarily.

183
00:15:16,480 --> 00:15:18,920
The police suspect that
it's a front for money laundering.

184
00:15:19,920 --> 00:15:22,240
We have to wait
for the money trail to be verified.

185
00:15:24,240 --> 00:15:25,600
Well, well.

186
00:15:26,280 --> 00:15:29,320
I just slipped up and informed the police

187
00:15:29,400 --> 00:15:32,400
that your Fa Bancha mine
is a thieves' den.

188
00:15:32,480 --> 00:15:35,720
Oh, the police are
so proactive these days.

189
00:15:35,800 --> 00:15:37,160
You witch Madam.

190
00:15:37,240 --> 00:15:38,840
- Die!
- Dad, calm down.

191
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:41,240
- Officer, help!
- Die.

192
00:15:41,320 --> 00:15:42,640
- Let go. Dad, let go.
- Die!

193
00:15:42,720 --> 00:15:44,520
- You!
- Dad, calm down.

194
00:15:45,120 --> 00:15:46,160
He's trying to kill me.

195
00:15:46,240 --> 00:15:47,280
I'm filing another charge.

196
00:15:47,360 --> 00:15:49,800
Yes, I want to kill you.

197
00:15:49,880 --> 00:15:52,560
Dad, get it together. Calm down.

198
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:56,200
That would be difficult, Attorney,

199
00:15:56,280 --> 00:15:59,920
because the suspect showed violence,
assaulting Madam Krongsuk in front of us.

200
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:03,280
I'm afraid granting his bail would be
dangerous for the aggrieved party.

201
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:04,440
Officer.

202
00:16:04,520 --> 00:16:07,240
That madam
intentionally provoked my father!

203
00:16:07,320 --> 00:16:09,960
Just investigate
how vile and terrible she is!

204
00:16:16,280 --> 00:16:17,280
Damn it.

205
00:16:35,520 --> 00:16:36,600
<i>Pin!</i>

206
00:16:39,880 --> 00:16:40,960
Pin!

207
00:16:44,320 --> 00:16:45,840
Where are you, Pin?

208
00:16:47,400 --> 00:16:48,600
Pin.

209
00:16:50,320 --> 00:16:52,120
I want to go home.

210
00:16:53,120 --> 00:16:53,960
Pin!

211
00:16:54,040 --> 00:16:55,920
Mom.

212
00:16:57,960 --> 00:16:58,800
Mom.

213
00:16:58,880 --> 00:17:00,200
Pin?

214
00:17:00,960 --> 00:17:02,000
What's wrong?

215
00:17:02,600 --> 00:17:06,160
Jin. Mom is still stuck there.

216
00:17:07,240 --> 00:17:09,319
She couldn't come back to me.

217
00:17:10,800 --> 00:17:11,880
Pin.

218
00:17:15,520 --> 00:17:18,800
You're grieving her,
so you dreamed about her.

219
00:17:19,520 --> 00:17:20,839
It's okay.

220
00:17:24,119 --> 00:17:25,000
Pin.

221
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:27,680
Your mom was a good person.

222
00:17:28,280 --> 00:17:30,360
She will be in a better place.

223
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:34,480
I'm so sorry for her.

224
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:38,960
Pin.

225
00:17:48,400 --> 00:17:52,520
After walking practice, I'll take care of
those wounds and put on fresh dressings.

226
00:17:52,600 --> 00:17:56,240
I've Googled it all
and remembered every step.

227
00:17:57,080 --> 00:17:58,200
I can take care of myself.

228
00:18:00,600 --> 00:18:02,720
Why would you need
to take care of yourself?

229
00:18:02,800 --> 00:18:04,800
I can take care of you.

230
00:18:04,880 --> 00:18:08,560
I'm willing. I assure you,
I'm far more capable than Pin.

231
00:18:09,160 --> 00:18:10,960
You know I'm not a gentleman.

232
00:18:11,040 --> 00:18:12,840
Don't think I'll appreciate what you did.

233
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:14,400
You're still that witch's niece.

234
00:18:17,520 --> 00:18:21,600
Mr. Yai, I've cut ties with Auntie.

235
00:18:21,680 --> 00:18:23,080
I chose to be on your side.

236
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:27,960
If you just give me a chance,
I'm ready to change for the better.

237
00:18:28,040 --> 00:18:30,440
However you want me to be,
however you like,

238
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:32,560
just tell me, and I'll be like that.

239
00:18:40,160 --> 00:18:42,320
Why do you need to honk that loud?

240
00:18:42,920 --> 00:18:44,120
To bring you to your senses.

241
00:18:45,040 --> 00:18:46,800
Have you heard anything, Chief?

242
00:18:51,960 --> 00:18:54,000
There's a rumor that you died
falling into the ravine.

243
00:18:54,080 --> 00:18:56,040
And Pload had been arrested

244
00:18:56,120 --> 00:18:58,440
for conspiring with you to murder Unreuan.

245
00:18:58,520 --> 00:18:59,840
Mr. Yai didn't kill Un.

246
00:19:01,240 --> 00:19:02,200
How do you know?

247
00:19:02,280 --> 00:19:03,400
What did you see? Tell me.

248
00:19:03,480 --> 00:19:05,720
Well… Well…

249
00:19:05,800 --> 00:19:08,800
I just believe in you.

250
00:19:08,880 --> 00:19:10,960
There's no way you'd kill
a defenseless old woman.

251
00:19:13,560 --> 00:19:15,240
I'll turn myself in,
so they release Uncle Pload.

252
00:19:15,320 --> 00:19:16,400
Wait.

253
00:19:16,480 --> 00:19:17,880
If you decide to go,

254
00:19:17,960 --> 00:19:21,560
you'd need evidence ready for a court
battle and not just walk in stupidly.

255
00:19:21,640 --> 00:19:22,920
Have you learned nothing from me?

256
00:19:30,560 --> 00:19:32,400
You want to better yourself, don't you?

257
00:19:56,960 --> 00:20:00,960
Well, Noi told me Pin moved in with you.

258
00:20:01,680 --> 00:20:03,240
So I'm here to visit her.

259
00:20:03,840 --> 00:20:05,240
Pin went to pay respects to her mom.

260
00:20:08,360 --> 00:20:11,360
Then, can I wait for her inside?

261
00:20:14,080 --> 00:20:18,120
These days, our society
is full of people who have no morals.

262
00:20:18,880 --> 00:20:20,760
Please don't be one of them.

263
00:20:21,480 --> 00:20:23,360
All your years of education
would be a waste.

264
00:20:39,080 --> 00:20:43,440
Miss On, after all this,
I think we should return to Bangkok.

265
00:20:43,520 --> 00:20:45,320
How much longer will you have to wait?

266
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:49,120
How many more months or years
before Mr. Na gets that said fortune? And…

267
00:20:49,200 --> 00:20:52,240
a beautiful lady like you
could have chosen to marry any millionaire

268
00:20:52,320 --> 00:20:54,520
or socialite, Miss On.

269
00:20:54,600 --> 00:20:56,840
- Watch your mouth!
- Miss On?

270
00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:59,160
Do you really think
I'm trying to win Na back

271
00:20:59,240 --> 00:21:01,960
because I want his money or his assets?

272
00:21:02,040 --> 00:21:04,480
I love Na! Do you hear me? I love Na!

273
00:21:04,560 --> 00:21:05,680
Miss On…

274
00:21:08,440 --> 00:21:12,720
One-sided love is so pitiful,
don't you think?

275
00:21:12,800 --> 00:21:17,240
Don't you realize by now
that Na is so infatuated with Pin.

276
00:21:17,320 --> 00:21:18,520
Shut your mouth.

277
00:21:19,680 --> 00:21:21,440
Oh, my. Ms. Nee, let go of Miss On.

278
00:21:21,520 --> 00:21:23,800
Hey. She just hurt you,
and you're still helping her?

279
00:21:23,880 --> 00:21:24,800
Are you dumb?

280
00:21:24,880 --> 00:21:27,080
- Let go! Hold her back.
- I'll slap you.

281
00:21:27,160 --> 00:21:28,960
- Yes, yes.
- You want to get slapped that bad?

282
00:21:29,040 --> 00:21:30,800
- Let go.
- Come here!

283
00:21:30,880 --> 00:21:32,040
- Miss On.
- Ms. Nee!

284
00:21:32,120 --> 00:21:34,800
- Miss On.
- Come at me. Let go!

285
00:21:34,880 --> 00:21:37,240
- Miss On, enough.
- Let me go!

286
00:21:37,320 --> 00:21:38,560
Let go!

287
00:21:44,720 --> 00:21:45,960
Where's Auntie?

288
00:21:56,480 --> 00:21:59,600
If you really want to change,
you need to go back to the farm

289
00:21:59,680 --> 00:22:02,760
and report back to me
on everything that's happening there.

290
00:22:03,600 --> 00:22:04,720
Auntie.

291
00:22:10,840 --> 00:22:13,280
What is it, my beautiful niece?

292
00:22:13,960 --> 00:22:15,720
Who are you talking to?

293
00:22:18,640 --> 00:22:22,760
Auntie, did you and that dirty pig
already sleep together?

294
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:29,400
- Disgusting. What were you thinking?
- Come here.

295
00:22:29,480 --> 00:22:30,520
Come here right now.

296
00:22:36,240 --> 00:22:37,520
Where have you been?

297
00:22:42,760 --> 00:22:44,520
Did you not hear what I asked?

298
00:22:48,880 --> 00:22:50,960
I've been crashing at my friend's.

299
00:22:51,040 --> 00:22:53,560
I hadn't paid my phone bill,
so I couldn't contact anyone.

300
00:22:53,640 --> 00:22:57,760
So how did you know
I was back on the farm?

301
00:22:59,240 --> 00:23:03,120
Well, the men at Mr. Tong's house told me.

302
00:23:09,360 --> 00:23:11,080
And why are you so scared of me right now?

303
00:23:12,880 --> 00:23:14,600
I'm scared of Mr. Tong.

304
00:23:20,600 --> 00:23:22,640
He's under my thumb now.

305
00:23:23,240 --> 00:23:24,480
You don't need to be scared.

306
00:23:25,400 --> 00:23:27,560
Just act like a normal human being

307
00:23:28,160 --> 00:23:30,480
and don't cause me any more headaches.

308
00:23:33,800 --> 00:23:35,840
Wait for the day I become the farm owner.

309
00:23:37,200 --> 00:23:40,520
You and Na will get larger shares
from selling the farm

310
00:23:40,600 --> 00:23:42,480
than you could ever imagine.

311
00:23:53,520 --> 00:23:55,040
That's impossible.

312
00:23:55,120 --> 00:23:57,240
If Nee had really gone to my house,

313
00:23:57,880 --> 00:24:00,680
my men would have reported it to me,

314
00:24:00,760 --> 00:24:05,640
because I told them
you're looking for your daughter.

315
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:12,360
Tong has moved into the farm, Mr. Yai.

316
00:24:12,440 --> 00:24:14,160
I was looking around

317
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:17,320
and saw that he brought all his men here
to take control of the workers.

318
00:24:20,200 --> 00:24:21,360
What about your aunt?

319
00:24:21,880 --> 00:24:23,280
What is she about to do?

320
00:24:23,360 --> 00:24:24,440
What's her next move?

321
00:24:24,520 --> 00:24:27,520
Well, there's nothing yet.

322
00:24:27,600 --> 00:24:30,440
- Just be careful.
- <i>Yes.</i>

323
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:36,960
Who were you talking to?

324
00:24:37,040 --> 00:24:38,240
Give it back.

325
00:24:38,320 --> 00:24:40,320
Hey, why did you lie to me, Nee?

326
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:42,160
You didn't go to Mr. Tong's house.

327
00:24:51,440 --> 00:24:53,720
I asked, who were you talking to?

328
00:24:54,800 --> 00:24:57,640
If you won't tell me, I'll just kill you!

329
00:25:00,040 --> 00:25:02,640
The same way you killed Un?

330
00:25:06,840 --> 00:25:10,280
How did you know about that? Or that day…

331
00:25:32,840 --> 00:25:34,320
Was it you?

332
00:25:35,640 --> 00:25:41,000
You killed Aunt Un,
Uncle Paisal, and Dad too!

333
00:25:41,080 --> 00:25:42,320
I already know everything!

334
00:25:42,400 --> 00:25:43,920
Shut up!

335
00:25:46,040 --> 00:25:49,320
Because of you… and Na,

336
00:25:50,320 --> 00:25:52,200
my hands had to get stained with blood.

337
00:25:55,600 --> 00:25:56,800
Help!

338
00:26:05,640 --> 00:26:07,040
Mom.

339
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:12,080
I'm here to see you.

340
00:26:13,200 --> 00:26:15,240
You don't need to worry about me anymore.

341
00:26:17,360 --> 00:26:18,880
I can carry on with my life.

342
00:26:21,440 --> 00:26:23,920
I won't let your death be for nothing.

343
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:31,480
I will find the one who hurt you.

344
00:26:35,080 --> 00:26:38,080
I'll make sure they pay dearly
for what they've done.

345
00:26:43,680 --> 00:26:45,880
Please ascend to Heaven.

346
00:26:49,520 --> 00:26:51,720
You don't need to worry anymore.

347
00:27:17,360 --> 00:27:19,760
Hey, what happened to the truck?

348
00:27:19,840 --> 00:27:21,480
The tire probably blew.

349
00:27:21,560 --> 00:27:23,200
But I just got it changed yesterday.

350
00:27:23,280 --> 00:27:24,520
Go look.

351
00:27:26,040 --> 00:27:27,040
Come here.

352
00:27:36,960 --> 00:27:39,960
I don't see any nails. So how did it pop?

353
00:27:40,040 --> 00:27:41,120
What do we do, bro?

354
00:27:41,200 --> 00:27:44,760
If we stop and change the tire right here,
someone might see Ms. Tatsanee.

355
00:27:49,160 --> 00:27:50,320
I'll take the shortcut.

356
00:27:50,880 --> 00:27:53,760
You change the tire
and come pick me up at the warehouse.

357
00:27:54,360 --> 00:27:55,200
Bring her out.

358
00:27:56,040 --> 00:27:57,440
Hey, come here.

359
00:28:01,120 --> 00:28:02,960
What warehouse? I don't want to go there.

360
00:28:03,040 --> 00:28:03,960
Let go!

361
00:28:12,600 --> 00:28:13,440
Hey.

362
00:28:13,520 --> 00:28:15,400
Are you going to kill me
and leave me in the woods?

363
00:28:23,280 --> 00:28:24,560
Keep walking.

364
00:28:25,240 --> 00:28:26,400
Shut your mouth.

365
00:28:27,120 --> 00:28:28,160
Ms. Nee?

366
00:28:33,200 --> 00:28:34,320
Where's my phone?

367
00:28:42,440 --> 00:28:43,520
Go!

368
00:28:45,600 --> 00:28:47,240
Don't even try to escape,

369
00:28:47,320 --> 00:28:49,920
because all the workers here
work for Mr. Tong now.

370
00:28:51,040 --> 00:28:53,120
Then untie me.

371
00:28:53,200 --> 00:28:56,880
How am I supposed to eat with my hands
tied up? If I starve to death,

372
00:28:56,960 --> 00:28:58,720
Auntie won't spare any of you.

373
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:01,560
Hey.

374
00:29:12,720 --> 00:29:14,000
We're off work.

375
00:29:14,080 --> 00:29:15,360
I'm gonna go find something
to shove in my face.

376
00:29:15,440 --> 00:29:16,760
Wanna come with us?

377
00:29:16,840 --> 00:29:17,840
You guys have fun.

378
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:19,080
I'll head back to Paisal Farm soon.

379
00:29:19,160 --> 00:29:20,120
Go.

380
00:29:20,840 --> 00:29:21,960
- Let's go.
- That shop. Go.

381
00:29:22,040 --> 00:29:23,480
Eat some for me too.

382
00:29:23,560 --> 00:29:25,440
- Check the truck.
- Yes, bro.

383
00:29:46,320 --> 00:29:48,040
Bro, there's smoke!

384
00:29:48,880 --> 00:29:50,480
What idiot's burning grass out here?

385
00:29:54,360 --> 00:29:56,000
Grab the extinguishers.

386
00:29:56,080 --> 00:29:58,360
If it reaches the warehouse,
we're all screwed. Go!

387
00:30:42,080 --> 00:30:44,440
Yes, Boss. I've locked her up.

388
00:30:45,480 --> 00:30:48,360
Find the right opportunity to silence her.

389
00:30:53,200 --> 00:30:55,440
But Madam told me
to keep her here and nothing else.

390
00:30:55,520 --> 00:30:57,200
You little shit!

391
00:30:57,280 --> 00:31:00,680
Yes, Boss. I'll do as you order.

392
00:31:05,840 --> 00:31:06,760
Let's go.

393
00:31:34,960 --> 00:31:37,680
Paisal Farm will be mine.

394
00:31:48,640 --> 00:31:49,760
Let's do it, bro.

395
00:32:05,520 --> 00:32:06,600
Someone must have helped her escape.

396
00:32:06,680 --> 00:32:08,000
Search the area! Go!

397
00:32:12,160 --> 00:32:13,960
‪Come on, hurry.

398
00:32:15,200 --> 00:32:17,600
Pin, how did you know I was here?

399
00:32:17,680 --> 00:32:19,560
Don't ask me yet. Just run.

400
00:32:19,640 --> 00:32:20,800
I parked over there.

401
00:32:24,080 --> 00:32:24,880
There they are!

402
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,000
You hold them off.

403
00:32:32,920 --> 00:32:35,440
If you run through that open area,
they'll find you.

404
00:32:36,680 --> 00:32:39,120
If you don't want to die, follow me.

405
00:32:39,720 --> 00:32:41,320
Pin! Wait for me!

406
00:32:57,680 --> 00:33:00,040
Where's your phone? Call someone for help.

407
00:33:00,120 --> 00:33:01,680
I forgot to bring it.

408
00:33:06,600 --> 00:33:10,360
We have to wait here until it's dark,
then we'll find a way to shake them off.

409
00:33:12,760 --> 00:33:14,160
Why did you come help me?

410
00:33:14,240 --> 00:33:15,920
Don't tell me you were worried about me.

411
00:33:16,000 --> 00:33:16,960
I don't believe you.

412
00:33:18,240 --> 00:33:19,720
You always love playing the saint.

413
00:33:20,320 --> 00:33:22,600
Only men who want to get with you
would fall for that.

414
00:33:24,200 --> 00:33:28,560
I risked my life helping you
because that day, you called me

415
00:33:28,640 --> 00:33:30,360
and told me to go save Mom.

416
00:33:30,440 --> 00:33:31,680
How did you know?

417
00:33:32,360 --> 00:33:33,600
Who killed my mom?

418
00:33:33,680 --> 00:33:35,160
You saw her, didn't you?

419
00:33:35,240 --> 00:33:36,600
Ms. Nee, tell me.

420
00:33:36,680 --> 00:33:37,920
I don't know anything.

421
00:33:38,520 --> 00:33:41,280
If you want to stay here
waiting for them to kill you, go head.

422
00:33:41,360 --> 00:33:42,760
Ms. Nee.

423
00:33:43,960 --> 00:33:46,520
Ms. Nee. Don't move.

424
00:33:47,600 --> 00:33:48,760
Ms. Nee.

425
00:33:49,480 --> 00:33:50,440
Ms. Nee!

426
00:33:54,480 --> 00:33:55,360
Over there.

427
00:34:00,880 --> 00:34:03,440
Pin! That snake just bit you.

428
00:34:06,440 --> 00:34:07,640
I'm okay.

429
00:34:07,720 --> 00:34:11,040
Ms. Nee, get out of here
and bring someone to help me.

430
00:34:11,639 --> 00:34:13,159
Pin, are you crazy?

431
00:34:13,239 --> 00:34:15,800
Why did you help me? You could have died.

432
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,040
No, Pin.

433
00:34:20,199 --> 00:34:22,280
You can't die, Pin. Pin.

434
00:34:23,639 --> 00:34:25,199
What do I do?

435
00:34:26,840 --> 00:34:28,080
Hey.

436
00:34:44,320 --> 00:34:46,840
Go! Hurry!

437
00:34:52,719 --> 00:34:54,920
Help! Help us!

438
00:34:55,000 --> 00:34:58,200
Pin's been bitten by a snake! Help! Help!

439
00:34:58,280 --> 00:34:59,320
Pin.

440
00:35:03,040 --> 00:35:04,760
Did you lock Tatsanee up securely?

441
00:35:07,640 --> 00:35:09,600
What happened to my niece?

442
00:35:09,680 --> 00:35:11,720
And why are you
covered in blood like this?

443
00:35:13,600 --> 00:35:14,640
What happened to Tatsanee?

444
00:35:17,400 --> 00:35:19,720
Answer me! Now!

445
00:35:36,320 --> 00:35:39,760
The clean cash from the pub for this month
has already been wired, Boss.

446
00:35:42,280 --> 00:35:44,320
- Good.
- Boss.

447
00:35:46,160 --> 00:35:48,320
Hey. Wait.

448
00:35:48,400 --> 00:35:52,320
That… That's a gun. And I'm your man.

449
00:35:52,400 --> 00:35:53,800
Show me some respect.

450
00:35:53,880 --> 00:35:57,800
You're planning to kill Nee,
so how are we supposed to stay together?!

451
00:35:58,680 --> 00:36:00,000
Calm down.

452
00:36:00,080 --> 00:36:01,800
I was only trying to help.

453
00:36:01,880 --> 00:36:04,920
Tatsanee knows your secrets, Madam.

454
00:36:05,960 --> 00:36:08,680
If she slipped up,
we'd all end up in prison.

455
00:36:08,760 --> 00:36:10,480
But Nee is my niece.

456
00:36:10,560 --> 00:36:11,760
Hold on.

457
00:36:11,840 --> 00:36:14,800
She's just your niece, not your daughter.

458
00:36:19,600 --> 00:36:20,480
Hey.

459
00:36:23,440 --> 00:36:26,800
I was a bit thoughtless. I'm sorry.

460
00:36:26,880 --> 00:36:29,640
Put down the gun first. Yeah.

461
00:36:31,560 --> 00:36:34,640
Yes, Madam. We shouldn't fight
among ourselves now.

462
00:36:34,720 --> 00:36:37,120
Pinanong already helped
Ms. Tatsanee escape.

463
00:36:37,200 --> 00:36:38,080
Hey.

464
00:36:39,520 --> 00:36:41,520
What did you just say? Pin?

465
00:36:41,600 --> 00:36:42,760
How did she just show up?

466
00:36:44,320 --> 00:36:48,960
So… if your niece tells Pinanong

467
00:36:49,040 --> 00:36:50,840
that you killed Unreuan,

468
00:36:52,520 --> 00:36:53,720
we're doomed.

469
00:36:56,040 --> 00:36:59,440
We need to find a way
to make Pload confess right away

470
00:36:59,520 --> 00:37:01,320
in court that he killed Un,

471
00:37:01,880 --> 00:37:03,000
so we can walk away from this.

472
00:37:07,240 --> 00:37:08,760
Yai died because of your mom.

473
00:37:10,400 --> 00:37:12,080
And now Pin almost died because of you.

474
00:37:13,080 --> 00:37:14,280
Why were you even born?

475
00:37:14,360 --> 00:37:15,520
Such a waste of space.

476
00:37:15,600 --> 00:37:19,320
So what? This is who I am.

477
00:37:19,400 --> 00:37:21,800
A terrible, envious person.

478
00:37:21,880 --> 00:37:24,840
I hate how Pin always pretended
to be innocent.

479
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:26,640
I hate everything about her.

480
00:37:26,720 --> 00:37:28,080
But you know what?

481
00:37:30,480 --> 00:37:32,720
Pin never abandoned me.

482
00:37:32,800 --> 00:37:35,800
She put her life on the line to save mine.

483
00:37:35,880 --> 00:37:37,280
Why did she even do that?!

484
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:39,200
She must be insane!

485
00:37:39,280 --> 00:37:40,400
She's supposed to hate me!

486
00:37:40,480 --> 00:37:42,840
She should have wanted
to take her revenge, right?!

487
00:37:53,160 --> 00:37:56,680
We don't need reasons
to do good, Tatsanee.

488
00:38:02,840 --> 00:38:05,720
Nurse. How is Pin doing?

489
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:08,720
Please save Pin. Please save her.

490
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:12,720
- Yes.
- Or…

491
00:38:13,520 --> 00:38:15,760
I should get Mr. Yai here to check on Pin.

492
00:38:17,120 --> 00:38:19,600
Have you lost your mind? Yai's dead.

493
00:38:19,680 --> 00:38:21,680
Mr. Yai is still alive!

494
00:38:23,400 --> 00:38:24,360
Mr. Yai?

495
00:38:25,880 --> 00:38:27,080
You can't go out right now, ma'am.

496
00:38:30,400 --> 00:38:32,480
We need to keep monitoring you, ma'am.

497
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:36,720
Pin? Pin.

498
00:38:37,320 --> 00:38:39,200
Is Mr. Yai really still alive?

499
00:38:40,560 --> 00:38:42,280
Tell me the truth, Ms. Nee.

500
00:38:42,360 --> 00:38:44,160
Where is he?

501
00:39:02,520 --> 00:39:04,760
No, please don't shoot.

502
00:39:04,840 --> 00:39:07,480
Chief! No, Chief. He's on our side.

503
00:39:07,560 --> 00:39:09,880
Hey. Yai.

504
00:39:09,960 --> 00:39:11,720
Hey. Is this really you?

505
00:39:12,680 --> 00:39:14,080
Maybe I'm a ghost.

506
00:39:14,160 --> 00:39:15,960
So how did you know I'm here?

507
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:06,200
Thanks to Mr. Paisal for keeping you safe.

508
00:40:07,160 --> 00:40:08,920
I would have been a corpse,

509
00:40:09,520 --> 00:40:11,160
if it weren't for Tatsanee's help.

510
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:24,880
- Pin, Pin.
- Hey, Pin.

511
00:40:26,680 --> 00:40:30,000
Pin got bitten by a snake, but they've
her the anti-venom already. Look at her.

512
00:40:30,080 --> 00:40:32,160
She wouldn't rest, and she was
hell-bent on coming to see you.

513
00:40:32,240 --> 00:40:35,120
She's pregnant. Why did you guys
let her run around like this?

514
00:40:35,760 --> 00:40:37,080
Careful, Mr. Yai.

515
00:40:37,960 --> 00:40:39,840
The obstetrician lives nearby.
I'll bring her.

516
00:40:46,040 --> 00:40:48,520
Doctor, how's the baby in her womb?

517
00:40:49,600 --> 00:40:51,200
The patient isn't pregnant.

518
00:40:52,560 --> 00:40:55,480
She passed out from exhaustion.

519
00:40:56,080 --> 00:40:57,000
I examined the snake bite.

520
00:40:57,080 --> 00:40:58,360
There's no inflammation.

521
00:40:58,440 --> 00:41:01,320
I'll prescribe some vitamin supplements.

522
00:41:01,400 --> 00:41:05,520
Just let her get plenty of rest,
and she'll be fine.

523
00:41:07,920 --> 00:41:09,240
Thank you so much, Doctor Yun.

524
00:41:09,320 --> 00:41:12,440
Come on, take some
of my homemade gac fruit juice

525
00:41:12,520 --> 00:41:13,480
back for your mother.

526
00:41:14,080 --> 00:41:15,680
Pin isn't pregnant.

527
00:41:16,200 --> 00:41:18,000
So she lied to you?

528
00:41:27,440 --> 00:41:29,720
Thank you so much for helping Yai.

529
00:41:32,680 --> 00:41:33,680
Hey, what's wrong?

530
00:41:36,040 --> 00:41:37,320
It's none of your business.

531
00:41:37,400 --> 00:41:38,200
Stay out of it.

532
00:41:40,320 --> 00:41:41,160
You…

533
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:14,000
What's wrong with me?

534
00:42:17,480 --> 00:42:19,040
You're just a deceitful woman.

535
00:42:28,400 --> 00:42:30,240
Still better than being a murderer.

536
00:42:34,360 --> 00:42:36,120
You made me believe
you were pregnant with Jom's child.

537
00:42:36,200 --> 00:42:37,320
What were you thinking?

538
00:42:37,400 --> 00:42:38,720
What did you even do that for, Pin?

539
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:42,440
You knew.

540
00:42:42,520 --> 00:42:46,200
You think I'm an idiot
that you can manipulate all you want?

541
00:42:46,880 --> 00:42:51,120
In all the time I've known you,
was there ever a single real moment, Pin?

542
00:42:55,240 --> 00:42:56,600
Puny Pin,

543
00:42:57,120 --> 00:43:00,480
the innocent crybaby
I once knew, is probably gone.

544
00:43:03,520 --> 00:43:07,360
Your mind is twisted. It doesn't match
the beauty of your name at all.

545
00:43:09,760 --> 00:43:10,960
That day at the hospital,

546
00:43:11,520 --> 00:43:14,640
I was going to tell you
I wasn't pregnant, but…

547
00:43:14,720 --> 00:43:16,320
You let Jom say all that.

548
00:43:19,160 --> 00:43:20,680
You didn't deny it.

549
00:43:20,760 --> 00:43:22,920
That meant you went along with it.

550
00:43:24,760 --> 00:43:28,880
I couldn't help but think
that if I stayed with you,

551
00:43:28,960 --> 00:43:32,520
Madam would never stop
using Mom to hurt you.

552
00:43:34,880 --> 00:43:36,840
So you just let everything play out?

553
00:43:36,920 --> 00:43:40,080
You let Jom mock me for being a fool?

554
00:43:40,160 --> 00:43:42,280
You let him say you were carrying
the baby from an affair?

555
00:43:43,400 --> 00:43:45,080
I never had an affair.

556
00:43:45,960 --> 00:43:47,480
I've never slept with Jom.

557
00:43:47,560 --> 00:43:49,240
Then why did you lie to me?!

558
00:43:50,640 --> 00:43:52,120
You were so cruel to me.

559
00:43:52,200 --> 00:43:53,920
How could you be this cruel to me?

560
00:43:54,000 --> 00:43:56,600
I hate you!
Do you hear me? I hate you, Pin!

561
00:44:38,200 --> 00:44:40,560
I saw Auntie kill your mom.

562
00:44:40,640 --> 00:44:43,080
Didn't you go pick up Aunt Pen?
Where's Aunt Pen?

563
00:44:43,160 --> 00:44:45,120
Damn it!

564
00:44:45,200 --> 00:44:47,720
Krongsuk, either you or I have to die.

565
00:44:47,800 --> 00:44:50,240
<i>You want to see me</i>
<i>become a monster so badly? Fine.</i>

566
00:44:50,840 --> 00:44:53,720
I also want to know if you still want me.

567
00:44:53,800 --> 00:44:55,680
I'll let you have her, Mr. Tong.

568
00:44:55,760 --> 00:44:59,560
Auntie! What are you going to do to Pin?
She saved me, Auntie!

569
00:45:42,360 --> 00:45:44,640
Subtitle translation by: Anan Pratchayakul
